{"tid":266013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"on鳩仔謝霆峰8500萬買淺水灣怡峰 呎價近4.4萬","createTime":"2017-06-01T06:46:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-01T08:27:54.000Z","uid":51121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d3c000dbce9ddafca313bd61aa5c32fc2937299","tid":266013,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:46:28.000Z","msg":"淺水灣道單棟低密度住宅怡峰，日前獲知名藝人謝賢承接。<br />\n<br />\n利嘉閣地產梁志偉表示，該單位為怡峰低層A室，實用面積約1,939方呎，為兩房兩廳連一個套房間隔。原業主開價8,800萬元，經議價下減約300萬元，減幅逾3%，終以8,500萬元獲承接，實用面積呎價43,837元。<br />\n<br />\n土地註冊處資料顯示，單位於本月中成交，登記買家為謝家鈺(TSE KA YUK PATRICK)，與謝賢的原名相同。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，原業主於2007年8月，以約4,500萬元購入，持貨至今成功轉售，獲利約4,000萬元，物業升幅約89%。梁志偉補充，上述為該怡峰於5月份錄得的首宗二手成交，而現時屋苑並沒有任何盤源提供"},{"pid":"c9bc87f3a42bbf3fc3cfaa54d4293d585fbfc3f7","tid":266013,"uid":108238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:52:47.000Z","msg":"佢老豆買關佢咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660f6b002196a1beb079658b57977ebcb33ec804","tid":266013,"uid":51121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:55:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢老豆買關佢咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢老豆燃有收入.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f442d02851c636cb31355b92239ab4f47805304","tid":266013,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:57:43.000Z","msg":"唔比遲些升到10萬一呎?"},{"pid":"685380552735aa25022f6ef56a7d3d097304ac43","tid":266013,"uid":86117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:58:31.000Z","msg":"葡萄撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bfa6a0cef67db8f7c30b123fc855243e66a2bb9","tid":266013,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T07:00: